_sText:
This is a version of a map still in development. The final course will be way longer.

Featuring:
- Spawn Area
- 4 playable levels of the "Easy" path

Known bugs:
- Platforms collide with walls in level 3
- Levels can be seen through the skybox in the spawn area

Recommended settings:
sv_accelerate 8
sv_airaccelerate 100

Music:
Silent Hill 2 - Laura Plays The Piano
